data.description: A military relocation is the only reason this family is leaving their dream home!  Largest model in Mayfield (The Cornell), no longer available through the builder. BETTER THAN NEW! Closed December 31, 2022 and only lived in for 7 months, this home offers a transferable warranty and already has many amenities not included in the price of a brand new home, including over $100,000 in upgrades and a FINISHED BASEMENT which adds an additional 1700 sq. ft.!  With five bedrooms, five baths, great room, office, loft, upstairs laundry, an expanded covered patio, three car garage, fully fenced yard, and finished basement, this home has everything you need and more. Live in luxury with main level ameniteis such as private study with french doors and custom built ins, Chef's kitchen with oversized island, walk in pantry and separate butler/coffee station, open concept living and dining with gas fireplace, a separate entry area from your three car garage with walk in coat closet, as well as main floor bedroom and full bath. Upstairs enjoy extra space in the loft, along with generous primary suite with large walk in closet and five piece bath, upstairs laundry, and three additional bedrooms with two additional full baths. In the fully finished basement, enjoy 1700 sq. ft. of extra living space with a full bath. Outside, enjoy your expanded covered patio with gas line and fully fenced yard backing to greenbelt. Store all your vehicles and toys in your fully insulated oversized three car garage with electric car charging station and overhead storage shelves. Don't miss out on the only home this size available in this beautiful and conveniently located community.  To see features and floorplans, visit https://www.centurycommunities.com/find-your-new-home/colorado/denver-metro/thornton/mayfield/plans/cornell--residence-50255.
